df.pca<-data.frame(env.pca$x)
rownames(env.pc)==metadata_soil$sample_id
## logical(0)
df.pca$Nlevel<-metadata_soil$N
df.pca$Nadd<-metadata_soil$Nregime

sum.pca<-summary(env.pca)
xlab=paste0("PC1(",round(sum.pca$importance[2,1]*100,2),"%)")
ylab=paste0("PC2(",round(sum.pca$importance[2,2]*100,2),"%)")

# Extract loadings (coefficients) of the principal components
loadings <- env.pca$rotation

# Calculate scaling factor for arrow lengths
scale_factor <- sqrt(env.pca$sdev)

# Scale loadings to adjust arrow lengths
scaled_loadings <- loadings * scale_factor

scaled_loadings_df<-as.data.frame(scaled_loadings)
scaled_loadings_df$Variable <- rownames(scaled_loadings_df)
#df.pca$site_type <- as.factor(df.pca$site_type)
col11<-c("darkgrey","chartreuse","deepskyblue","darkviolet","darkorange","#CC0033","darkgoldenrod")
#lines<-c("Ncont"="dotted","Ncess"="solid")
shape = c("Ncont" = 17, "Ncess" = 19)
library(colorRamps)
p <- ggplot(df.pca) +
  geom_point(size = 7, alpha = 0.8,
             aes(x = PC1, y = PC2,
                 colour = as.factor(df.pca$Nlevel),linetype=Nadd,shape=Nadd))+ 
  # 
  scale_colour_manual(values=col11,
                      labels=c(expression(0),expression(2),
                               expression(5),expression(10),
                               expression(15),expression(20),
                               expression(50)
                      )
  )+
  scale_shape_manual(
    values = shape,
    labels = c(
      expression(N[cont]),  # Ncont -> N_cont
      expression(N[cess])   # Ncess -> N_cess
    )
  ) +
  geom_segment(data = scaled_loadings_df,
               aes(x = 0, y = 0, xend = PC1*10, yend = PC2*10),
               arrow = arrow(length = unit(0.02, "npc")),
               linewidth = 0.8,
               colour = "grey") +
  
  geom_text_repel(data = scaled_loadings_df,
                  aes(x = PC1*10, y = PC2*10, label = Variable),
                  colour = "black",
                  size = 5) +
  
  labs(x = xlab, y = ylab) +theme_bw()+guides(
    colour = guide_legend(title = expression(N[level])),
    shape = guide_legend(title = expression(N[history])),    # Nadd -> N_add
    linetype = guide_legend(title = expression(N[history]))  # 
  ) +
  annotate("text",
           x = mean(range(df.pca$PC1)),  # x
           y = max(df.pca$PC2) * 1.1,    # y
           label = "Antibiotic biosynthesis genes (ABG)",
           hjust = 0.5,  # 
           vjust = 0,    # 
           size = 6,     # 
           fontface = "bold",  # 
           color = "black")+
  theme(
    text = element_text(size = 16, family = "sans"),
    axis.text = element_text(colour = "black", size = 16, face = "bold"),
    axis.title = element_text(colour = "black", size = 16, face = "bold"),
    panel.border = element_rect(fill = NA, color = "black", size = 1.2),
    strip.text = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),  # 
    #  legend.position = "bottom",  # 
    legend.title = element_text(size = 16, face = "bold"),
    legend.text = element_text(size = 16)
  )
p<-p+theme(panel.border = element_rect(fill = NA,color = "black",size=1.5,linetype = "solid"))
p
